01:34:14.747 --> 01:34:16.256
Trenutek, po torbo grem.

01:34:44.460 --> 01:34:46.465
Socialna služba.

01:34:59.934 --> 01:35:02.948
Uporabila sta kartico,
ki jo je lastnik pustil v avtu.

01:35:03.188 --> 01:35:05.323
Na sever gresta
proti Kaliforniji.

01:35:05.981 --> 01:35:08.402
Vem, kam gresta.
–Dober večer.

01:35:18.869 --> 01:35:20.672
Gardner?

01:35:21.873 --> 01:35:23.676
Gardner!

