01:41:59.322 --> 01:42:02.453
Kendra! Pomagaj!

01:42:13.670 --> 01:42:15.591
Dobro, obrnimo ga.

01:42:15.921 --> 01:42:17.677
Takole.
–Obrni ga.

01:42:18.882 --> 01:42:21.019
Daj! Daj!

01:42:22.095 --> 01:42:23.934
Gardner!
–Zmogel boš!

01:42:26.140 --> 01:42:29.105
Ostani pri sebi!
Ne zapusti nas!

01:42:29.394 --> 01:42:31.234
Daj!

01:42:36.301 --> 01:42:37.759
Kakšna je bila?

01:42:40.988 --> 01:42:42.792
Moja mama.

01:42:49.064 --> 01:42:50.521
Neustrašna.

01:42:51.500 --> 01:42:53.386
Prijazna.

01:42:54.502 --> 01:42:59.391
In zdela se je nepremagljiva.

01:43:02.677 --> 01:43:05.893
Po njeni smrti
mi ni bilo več do življenja.

01:43:09.469 --> 01:43:10.926
Ljubil si jo.

01:43:12.229 --> 01:43:13.985
Ja, sem.

01:43:16.234 --> 01:43:17.690
Ti si moj oče.

01:43:19.319 --> 01:43:20.578
Ja, sem.

01:43:23.574 --> 01:43:27.751
Tam so!
–Hitro! Ni časa!

01:43:29.872 --> 01:43:33.800
Vedel sem, da te bom našel.
–Vse bo še dobro.

01:43:34.085 --> 01:43:37.929
Nisi sam.
Ostani z mano, Gardner.

01:43:39.173 --> 01:43:40.585
Pohitite!

01:44:17.546 --> 01:44:20.809
Predolgo traja.
Pritisk mu pada.

01:44:20.882 --> 01:44:22.970
Spraviti ga moram
z naše težnosti.

01:44:26.180 --> 01:44:28.067
Više morate leteti.

01:44:29.057 --> 01:44:31.478
Me razumeta?
–Veste, da ne smem.

01:44:31.560 --> 01:44:33.648
To je proti našim predpisom.

01:44:37.342 --> 01:44:38.753
Prevzel bom krmilo.

01:44:41.820 --> 01:44:44.917
Kaj počneš?
–Odpeljal nas bom v stratosfero.

01:44:44.990 --> 01:44:50.163
Prosim?
–Brez skrbi, prenesel bo.

01:44:51.038 --> 01:44:54.253
Ampak opozarjam vaju,
da bosta morda morala prevzeti.

01:44:54.333 --> 01:44:57.347
Midva …
–Mogoče je, da bom umrl.

01:44:57.628 --> 01:44:59.431
Ampak si to že počel?
–Sem.

01:44:59.547 --> 01:45:01.386
Pogosto.

01:45:01.716 --> 01:45:04.515
Virtualno. –Krasno.

01:45:04.551 --> 01:45:05.904
Pripni se.

01:45:06.721 --> 01:45:08.162
Pripnimo te.

01:45:08.765 --> 01:45:11.185
Pripravi se. Daj.
Primi pas.

01:45:11.769 --> 01:45:13.322
Prevzel sem krmilo.

01:45:39.212 --> 01:45:41.100
Ne, više moramo.

01:46:37.073 --> 01:46:38.661
Skušaj ga zbuditi.

01:46:39.524 --> 01:46:42.703
Gardner!
Gardner, zbudi se!

01:46:45.614 --> 01:46:48.082
Ne, ne, ne!

01:46:48.158 --> 01:46:50.128
Ostani privezana,
jaz bom prijela.

01:47:19.231 --> 01:47:22.447
Smo na mojem planetu?
–Nismo.

01:47:23.194 --> 01:47:25.247
Smo na tvojem?

01:47:26.347 --> 01:47:27.740
Nismo.

01:47:30.577 --> 01:47:32.729
Me boš kdaj nehala klofutati?

01:47:45.216 --> 01:47:49.559
Vrniti se moraš.
–Tulsa, nikar. –Ne maram tega.

01:47:50.722 --> 01:47:52.561
Ampak oba veva,

01:47:54.476 --> 01:47:55.965
da se moraš vrniti.

01:47:57.939 --> 01:47:59.742
Ljubim te, Tulsa.

01:48:00.984 --> 01:48:02.989
Tudi jaz te ljubim.

01:48:23.006 --> 01:48:27.016
Kako je?
–Za zdaj je stabilen.

01:48:27.092 --> 01:48:29.099
Morali bi imeti dovolj časa.

01:48:29.179 --> 01:48:31.266
In ti?
Si dobro?

01:48:33.225 --> 01:48:35.229
Očitno sem.

01:48:36.228 --> 01:48:38.233
Dobro je vedeti.

01:49:09.511 --> 01:49:14.020
Pogrešala te bom, Gardner.
Najbolj od vsega.

01:49:18.186 --> 01:49:19.943
Tudi jaz te bom.

01:49:21.149 --> 01:49:23.154
Najboljša mama si,
ki je nisem imel.

01:49:26.529 --> 01:49:28.664
Srečno pot.

01:49:36.789 --> 01:49:38.177
Gospodična, počakajte!

01:49:38.751 --> 01:49:40.221
Ne smete sem.

01:49:45.172 --> 01:49:46.530
Mega prevoz.

01:49:49.176 --> 01:49:50.649
Boš dobro?

01:49:54.850 --> 01:49:56.689
Izjemna si.

01:49:57.935 --> 01:50:00.654
In s tabo sem se imel lepo,
kot še nikoli.

01:50:02.942 --> 01:50:06.868
Seveda ti tega
nočem povedati v obraz.

01:50:08.948 --> 01:50:10.418
Ravno si mi.

01:50:21.961 --> 01:50:26.018
<i>Deset, devet, osem,

01:50:26.800 --> 01:50:30.940
<i>sedem, šest, pet,

01:50:31.137 --> 01:50:34.317
<i>štiri, tri, dve.

01:50:35.225 --> 01:50:37.525
<i>Ena, nula.

01:50:38.353 --> 01:50:41.318
<i>Vžig, vzlet.

01:51:12.011 --> 01:51:14.693
Jutri ob isti uri?

01:51:14.707 --> 01:51:16.148
Meni je prav.

01:51:17.568 --> 01:51:19.025
Tulsa.

01:51:19.936 --> 01:51:21.359
Obisk imaš.

01:51:24.483 --> 01:51:27.201
<i>Adijo.</i>
–Iti moram.

01:51:39.832 --> 01:51:42.002
Kot veš,
sem se upokojila iz Nase.

01:51:42.251 --> 01:51:46.261
Ne povsem.
Zdaj vodim urjenje.

01:51:46.765 --> 01:51:48.221
Kar je super.

01:51:48.341 --> 01:51:52.220
Malo sem se morala privaditi
spet življenja na Zemlji.

01:51:53.430 --> 01:51:55.481
Zašla sem.

01:51:56.432 --> 01:52:00.655
Ker na Marsu šest let nisem
imela kje porabiti denarja,

01:52:00.729 --> 01:52:02.698
ga imam kar precej.

01:52:02.771 --> 01:52:06.948
V Boulderu v Koloradu
sem kupila ranč.

01:52:07.069 --> 01:52:10.283
Rada smučam,
ljudje so prijazni.

01:52:11.364 --> 01:52:15.292
Hiša je velika
in včasih sem osamljena.

01:52:16.494 --> 01:52:18.582
Bi želela živeti tam z mano?

01:52:23.752 --> 01:52:27.679
Vam plačuje,
da me vzamete?

01:52:28.090 --> 01:52:31.886
Kje pa!
Ne.

01:52:31.969 --> 01:52:34.188
Ker bom čez mesec dni
polnoletna.

01:52:35.972 --> 01:52:38.144
Kdo je omenil samo en mesec?

01:53:00.291 --> 01:53:02.212
<i>Želel sem si na Zemljo.

01:53:03.542 --> 01:53:06.472
<i>Ne le na obisk,
želel sem živeti tam.

01:53:07.631 --> 01:53:11.511
<i>Toda izkazalo se je,
da si ljudje na Zemlji želijo enako

01:53:11.592 --> 01:53:13.185
<i>kot ljudje z Marsa.

01:53:14.679 --> 01:53:19.899
<i>Kar zatrdno vem,
ker sem za zdaj še edini.

01:53:22.145 --> 01:53:26.072
<i>Ne vem, kje je bolje,
vem pa tole.

01:53:27.359 --> 01:53:29.198
<i>Lepo je biti doma.

